text:
My purpose is to be a
wise and visionary leader.

I want to inspire women to
pursue science, technology,

I will build others up
so that they can lead.

My purpose is to build the new
era of aerospace technology.

I want to help put a
human being on Mars,

and I want to make our
world a safer place.

My purpose is to revitalize
advanced manufacturing

in America, and ensure that
well-paying and meaningful jobs

are part of the
future of our country,
I want to make my family proud.

I want to build a
legacy dedicated

to the generations of Alabama
laborers and homemakers
